name: pixeled memories: not a flamethrower
description: pixels and the passage of time share a fundamental similarity. from a distanced perspective, both appear smooth and continuous. however, when viewed more closely, the individual and discrete entities can be distinguished as precious - in their own right. although j.w’s 25th year progressed swiftly, these pixeled moments were integral to the year’s passage and represent my favorite memories together. (5/6)
